  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2 17\u0d9a \u0d9a\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dc5 \u0d9c\u0d82\u0da2\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c 02\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd6",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "02 killed with Kerala ganja worth 17 crores",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Navy says that two suspects were arrested yesterday (20th) along with 575 kilos of Kerala Ganja worth over 172 million rupees along with 600 grams of Kerala Ganja worth over 172 million rupees in the sea area off old Kasiruna Veralathira in Jaffna Karainagar area.",
        "A group of officers belonging to the Northern Naval Command launched a special search operation in the sea off the old Kasurina beach in Karainagar, where a suspicious dinghy was spotted and the vessel was chased and raided.",
        "There, 575 kilos of 600 grams of Kerala ganja were found in 17 parcels hidden in the dinghy and the Navy took steps to arrest two suspects who were driving the dinghy.",
        "The traffickers have been arrested while bringing these Kerala ganja stocks from India by sea to sell to other parts of the island.",
        "The arrested suspects, aged 42 and 51, are residents of Jaffna Madagall areas and the Navy added that they have taken steps to hand over the suspects and the Kerala Ganja stock to Kites Police for further investigations."
      ],
